{"tid":981071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怒喝打尖大陸西","createTime":"2019-01-14T03:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T04:22:57.000Z","uid":189484,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab115951678803913b6da7a9227b5044e8ee580","tid":981071,"uid":189484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"尋晚等巴士返屋企, 架車會經過一間廢西酒店, 去到個站, 幾條大陸西痞係條街到吱吱喳喳又嘈又開gip, 車一黎就一堆人湧去車頭迫上車, 頭位個乘客(都係想擋住佢地咁款) 差d 比班陷家產推開, 睇圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMg2uJb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMg2uJb.png&h=b8fe434f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個時候, 我係中間大喝一聲<br />\n&quot;排隊啦吊你&quot;<br />\n幾條短命種立即縮返入呀媽個西度, 先行去龍尾排隊<br />\n<br />\n成班陷家產, 年紀又唔係大, 廿零三十歲行為衰到同d 中年大陸嬸一撚模樣, 仲諗住文革個班死晒後生會有改善, 點知係唔會. <br />\n香港人, 真係要守住自己條線, 唔可以忍"},{"pid":"4db6e5289bdb4a73626f2e2af5f1008bc77986ea","tid":981071,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"地鐵卡卡都發生緊 屌唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2b60e64b85fc61d0f4d4e6725fcf44b61fcc12","tid":981071,"uid":42426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4db6e5289bdb4a73626f2e2af5f1008bc77986ea","tid":981071,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"地鐵卡卡都發生緊 屌唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"好多廢老都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207df61207c7f8180f3f35ae3ea2f5dd089dc445","tid":981071,"uid":56432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"唔理真定假總之都係做個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21c1bfc57dd50c6c2db9ca14cec742fb3045b97","tid":981071,"uid":2383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"短命種呢個形容好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1af332f98740bed01394d5858759801f18e77e","tid":981071,"uid":189484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"有大陸西負皮"},{"pid":"a934e40817cc5929ed227025f70386f2de968290","tid":981071,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"大陸啲「公交車站」根本零秩序<br />\n成個站好撚長 成幾十米咁長<br />\n一個大範圍 十幾廿條公車線<br />\n啲車隨時可以起站頭或站尾開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊度開門啲人就一齊狗衝<br />\n所以亦無所謂排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港既排隊文明根本係out of佢地個腦<br />\n好似野人唔知有電腦一樣"}]}